{"tid":1742491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［好撚重要］唔想區選俾港共玩嘢延遲取消就入黎","createTime":"2019-11-20T22:32:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:47:18.000Z","uid":334292,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f05dcce976b3c59bd3e159a103e391a308cb463f","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:32:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講明先，呢個唔係啲乜中計po！<br />\n係想香港人起碼可以係區選將建制打鑊金！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n入正題之前，首先要介紹呢個人，因為呢個po嘅意見係佢最新一條片入面，片尾部分嘅香港應該點做。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">為何港警圍攻理大的七個理由 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/GPpC8vKjPJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGPpC8vKjPJs&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=2ed8583f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GPpC8vKjPJs</a></span><br />\n唐浩係一個Q&amp;A片入面有自介，佢係一個知名大學嘅新聞研究碩士（佢唔講邊間係因為避免中共騷擾佢母校加強統戰），<span style=\"color: red;\">早期係新聞傳播領域從事新聞研究，以前係財經雜誌研究員，資深記者，電視新聞主編，製作人，報社主筆</span>。詳細可以睇佢條youtube片<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-RNRy_Kf4nE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-RNRy_Kf4nE&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=748e09d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-RNRy_Kf4nE</a> <br />\n佢啲片好有邏輯，而且每次預測香港局勢幾乎次次中，呢個po嘅建議都係佢嘅，我大概將佢嘅建議打出黎姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢啲片都陸陸續續加緊英文字幕，文宣巴絲用下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好入正題，區選重要性好多人有講我就唔講啦，要講嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">點樣避免港共玩嘢搞區選</span>。主要要做兩樣嘢：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一：<span style=\"color: gold;\">出免責聲明，表明希望選舉順利舉行，絕對唔會阻礙選舉</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢係要大家係區選之前幾日低調，停一停。就算你幾睇唔起區選，佢<span style=\"color: red;\">始終都係一條戰線</span>，唔應該白白放棄，一定唔可以俾藉口港共延遲或者取消區選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以po免責聲明，性質同不自殺聲明一樣，表明唔會阻礙選舉，萬一有人咁做就絕對唔係示威者，係港共嘅政治伎倆</span></span>。絕對唔可以俾位港共入！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割席都要分清楚唔割邊個㗎嘛大佬，同裝修偷嘢就割嘅道理一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">投票前幾日甚至一個禮拜有人搞選舉辦事處，或者搞建制班垃圾嘅話一定要割</span></span>。你負皮都係咁話，係區選投票前搞班建制，搞選舉辦事處，或者選舉當日堵路除咗令到冇區選仲有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二：<span style=\"color: gold;\">投票前後嘅全部民調一律答投建制</span><br />\n</span><br />\n宜家呢個情勢，區選票數分佈一定會大改，而港共一定唔會放任建制票數大跌而出各種陰招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。區選前好可能會做<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">私人民調</span></span>，例如打電話果種，預測區選投票結果，結果極度不利嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">建制一定大量種票造假，或者搵藉口推遲選舉</span>。所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有電話打黎係投票嘅民調，無論佢係邊間機構，有幾黃都好，都唔好俾佢地知你投邊個，會唔會去投票！！唔好俾港共預測到投票結果 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />投完票之後，如果有統計人員問你投邊個都一樣，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一律答投建制</span></span>！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等建制班仆街以為自己冇咩事，結果仆曬街就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[size=6]11月24去投票，多你一個好重要[/size=6］<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"531cdfa39dcc8f00c0bf6bc09c97b115d50182c4","tid":1742491,"uid":279631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:34:52.000Z","msg":"推 !<br />\n另外，請入黎睇睇 :<br />\n今次區選已經變易等同公投, 港共正全力以赴過半數爭勝, 期望因此可以挾公投民意打壓運動。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741433</a>"},{"pid":"c662d95ab7593f6995e637803743f3e17e6b50f6","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:34:58.000Z","msg":"仆街最後打錯嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 補翻先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d89ceeba1c14a7f39e5b245f5efa1edcbb6e313","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:35:41.000Z","msg":"p牌絲推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943fd977844017a3653f6e95b58182792df8b0a0","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:36:23.000Z","msg":"同我推爆佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605d3f1832f20dd3bd09433a71bd7d2109f42150","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:37:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">11月24記得投票 多你一個好撚重要</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a050e550018acef57396b490b249ebc4860f2ae","tid":1742491,"uid":334292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:38:17.000Z","msg":"正經po唔好俾沉得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0eb8cf7076059d8fe8f4c6a600ea1312d2b2ce8","tid":1742491,"uid":202170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:49:58.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n1124見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6aa4b9ee88080748cd87a2b4b420505201859c","tid":1742491,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T22:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf8f7ac96b1bbd76a64b380938b42babb0230a5","tid":1742491,"uid":155837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a050e550018acef57396b490b249ebc4860f2ae","tid":